{"tid":847282,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉頓啲麵包真係唔多對路","createTime":"2018-10-04T05:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T17:23:07.000Z","uid":104454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"27f6e791135aebb5ec377104ad3baa510850a258","tid":847282,"uid":104454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"話說屋企有蟻患好耐<br />\n<br />\n啲野食一定要封好 如果唔係唔洗半個鐘一定有蟻<br />\n<br />\n同埋都慢慢了解左啲蟻既習性<br />\n<br />\n就係蟻其實係好識食 平野食係冇乜蟻<br />\n<br />\n但今日比我發現原來有啲野食竟然係會食死蟻<br />\n<br />\n就係嘉頓既麵包<br />\n<br />\n其實幾年前都試過有野食會食死啲蟻<br />\n<br />\n係一把魷魚乾 但都可以解讀成鹽份太高食死佢地<br />\n<br />\n但估唔到麵包都食得死蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底嘉頓啲麵包落左幾多化學野？<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，即刻比圖：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/131313_2a8ed4416d2bc6bc99a56ee6d17412a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F131313_2a8ed4416d2bc6bc99a56ee6d17412a2.png&h=8ffd1f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/131314_cd983f3b037908c01cb83847c7a82334.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F131314_cd983f3b037908c01cb83847c7a82334.png&h=f48a48d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都可以肯定係食死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未見過佢地係因為太逼或其他原因搞死自己"},{"pid":"155897f1b1f13f8ddb30c72f89f0ac02ee0a7c29","tid":847282,"uid":55413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"依家D麵包都好似係鹽分高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9169affcfaee01dbefc548a15d453b70c1c443","tid":847282,"uid":5793,"like":19,"dislike":7,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:20:08.000Z","msg":"睇撚錯嘉頓麵包會食死蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fee0acdbeb39db82209c517fe4b2df5dd0610b0","tid":847282,"uid":168911,"like":17,"dislike